title: RAW. Episode 3
creator_credit: C31 Melbourne, Stephen Wools, Josh Lefers, Nick McInerney and Big Dog Productions
brief_description: AIRED 19 April 2006. RAW is fast becoming a cult classic. The show follows Josh and Steve on urban adventures and into social experiments: from racing trams and street sweepers, to stealing bibles and creating a revolutionary system of economy with their epic Freeshit ManTM. These boys will do anything as long as it is ridiculous.
